                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18271206-124-off648 t18271206-124-cd649"></join>, 1 sovereign, and 9 shillings, the monies of 
                     <persName id="t18271206-124-victim730" type="victimName">
                        Charles 
                        Collard
                     <interp inst="t18271206-124-victim730" type="surname" value="Collard"></interp>
